    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and the upholstery is in great shape with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, shifts well, and all major electronics are fully functional. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
