    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the body panels are perfectly aligned with no dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that shows no wear and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a smooth-running engine, precise shifting, and a complete service history that confirms its meticulous upkeep.",
      "price": 49500.0,
